Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: java
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://adoptium.net/

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
# Mirrors the apk's proven runtime deps (ca-certificates-bundle libgcc libstdc++
# musl tzdata so:libasound.so.2) mapped to Debian trixie package names. Hardcoded
# because dh_shlibdeps is skipped for the prebuilt Adoptium binaries.
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ca-certificates,
 tzdata,
 libc6,
 libgcc-s1,
 libstdc++6,
 libasound2t64
Description: Eclipse Temurin @JAVA_TYPE@ @JAVA_MAJOR_VERSION@
 Eclipse Temurin is the open-source OpenJDK distribution from the Adoptium
 Working Group. This package provides the Temurin @JAVA_TYPE@ for the
 @JAVA_MAJOR_VERSION@ release line, installed under /@JAVA_DST_DIR@ with the
 runtime tools exposed on PATH via /usr/bin.

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-oci-config
Architecture: all
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: OCI configuration for @PACKAGE_NAME@
 OCI container configuration (JAVA_HOME and JAVA_VERSION environment
 variables) for the @PACKAGE_NAME@ package.

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-fips
Architecture: all
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: FIPS 140 configuration for @PACKAGE_NAME@
 BouncyCastle FIPS provider JARs, a BCFKS truststore generated from the
 bundled CA certificates, and the FIPS java.security / java.policy overrides
 for @PACKAGE_NAME@, installed under /usr/lib/bouncycastle.

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-fips-oci-config
Architecture: all
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@-fips (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: OCI FIPS configuration for @PACKAGE_NAME@
 OCI container configuration enabling FIPS mode (BouncyCastle module path,
 java.security overrides, approved-only mode) for @PACKAGE_NAME@.
